---
title: Pipeline Flow — ship.js State Machine
---

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> CheckGoals: ship.js starts

    CheckGoals --> NeedsPlan: no .goals.json
    CheckGoals --> FindPhase: .goals.json exists

    NeedsPlan --> DispatchPM: topic provided
    DispatchPM --> FindPhase: plan created

    FindPhase --> EmptyMajor: no sub-phases found
    FindPhase --> EvalState: sub-phase found
    FindPhase --> AllDone: no incomplete phases

    EmptyMajor --> DispatchPM: plan major phase
    DispatchPM --> FindPhase

    EvalState --> NeedsPlanPhase: no tasks
    EvalState --> NeedsBuild: tasks not-started
    EvalState --> Building: tasks in-progress
    EvalState --> AwaitingQA: all built
    EvalState --> QAFailed: tasks blocked
    EvalState --> Complete: all completed

    state NeedsPlanPhase {
        [*] --> CheckPlanFile
        CheckPlanFile --> PlanToTasks: plan file exists
        CheckPlanFile --> DispatchPMPlan: no plan file
        PlanToTasks --> [*]: tasks created (deterministic)
        DispatchPMPlan --> [*]: PM creates plan + tasks
    }

    NeedsPlanPhase --> NeedsBuild: tasks populated

    state NeedsBuild {
        [*] --> ValidatePlan
        ValidatePlan --> DistillBriefing: valid
        ValidatePlan --> SkipPhase: invalid
        DistillBriefing --> DispatchBuilder
        DispatchBuilder --> Reconcile: builder done
        Reconcile --> TestGate: statuses updated
        TestGate --> [*]
    }

    NeedsBuild --> AwaitingQA: reconciled → awaiting-qa
    NeedsBuild --> NeedsBuild: reconcile found untouched tasks

    state AwaitingQA {
        [*] --> DistillQA
        DistillQA --> DispatchQA
        DispatchQA --> [*]
    }

    AwaitingQA --> Complete: QA passes all
    AwaitingQA --> QAFailed: QA finds failures

    state QAFailed {
        [*] --> CheckRounds
        CheckRounds --> DispatchResolver: rounds < max
        CheckRounds --> EscalatePM: rounds >= max
        DispatchResolver --> AwaitingQA: fixed
        EscalatePM --> NeedsPlanPhase: PM revises
        EscalatePM --> HumanNeeded: 2x replan failed
    }

    state Complete {
        [*] --> TryMerge
        TryMerge --> NextPhase: more phases
        TryMerge --> ProjectDone: all phases done
    }

    Complete --> FindPhase: next phase
    AllDone --> [*]
    HumanNeeded --> [*]

    note right of Reconcile
        git diff → match task files[]
        Update .goals.json statuses
        Builder can't do this reliably
        in --print mode
    end note

    note right of PlanToTasks
        Deterministic parsing
        No LLM needed
        ### Task N: Title → add-task
    end note
